  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of the trial is to induce normal pubertal
      development in girls with Turner Syndrome in accordance with that of their peers and their
      individual state psychosocial maturation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
